{"tid":2025274,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史台】筆者搞左個有獎問答遊戲，答關於羅馬史題目有機會獲得電子書獎品","createTime":"2020-05-20T06:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T09:06:43.000Z","uid":120678,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0fccbfabc9c9b84ba3a60e7e895da503df2a41cc","tid":2025274,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"就讓筆者來扮演一次考試及評核局的角色，出一條關於古典史的題目刺激一下各位讀者的思考。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先講講遊戲規則：<br />\n本考題是可以帶回家的、可以打開書的take home open-book exam，限期是一星期，26/05西岸時間晚上11:59(中、港、台時間27/05下午2:59結束)。這題問題沒有標準答案，各位讀者均可以連登「正負評」機制，投票票選心水答覆。<br />\n<br />\n中文題目是：「羅馬帝國的衰亡促使了歐洲政治版圖的碎塊化，促進不同國家之間的競爭，對於近代歐洲文明的崛起利多於弊」你在多大程度上同意此說？試析述之(10分)<br />\n英文題目是：&quot;The decline and fall of the Roman Empire facilitated the political fragmentation of Europe, stimulated competition between countries, and brought more benefit than harms in the recent rise of European civilization to world domination&quot; To what extent do you agree with this statement? Please analyze. (10 Marks)<br />\n<br />\n參加者可以自由選擇以中文或英文作答。<br />\n<br />\n回覆獲最多淨讚好票數(正評減負評)的讀者，將可獲得由Zannanza's history channel送出的《超級工程：羅馬是怎樣建成的》電子書乙本，價值US$4。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位的參與！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72af7389534d6210ca74e4b742eba937d645a20a","tid":2025274,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過p牌俾唔到正負評"},{"pid":"00365216374c14f124d589f7b82a50045fe937c0","tid":2025274,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72af7389534d6210ca74e4b742eba937d645a20a","tid":2025274,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過p牌俾唔到正負評"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi